<ul><li><a href="https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pixel_density" title="Pixel density">Pixel density</a></li>
<li><a href="https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samples_per_inch" title="Samples per inch">Samples per inch</a> ŌĆō a related concept for <a href="https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Image_scanner" title="Image scanner">image scanners</a></li>
